name: Sky Blue
description:
Original tie dye tee in light blue. Each t-shirt has its own individual shade and circular tie dye pattern, perfect for this summer.

All of our tees are dyed with Dylon™ on 100% cotton Fruit of the Loom™ t-shirts.

Small 35"- 37" chest 
Medium 38"- 40" chest 
Large 41"-43" chest

We hope you'll love your Dynosaur tee as much as we do, however if you have any problems please contact dynsr@hotmail.co.uk.
